WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Models Zen 6’s 48 MB L3 per CCD and RDNA 4m’s WMMA AI instructions as
formulas, enabling GIOP to decide LMT shader dispatch size and FSR 4
upscaling preset based on available silicon.

